a woman, I am this, I am that”;

252
00:22:35,150 --> 00:22:42,730
“I am a bishop or I am a pope, 
I am this, I am that.”

253
00:22:44,190 --> 00:22:48,640
But once you are a realized soul, 
who will tell  you who arey ou?

254
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:52,970
Because the one which tells 
you is the mind which doesn’t exist

255
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:55,100
- no thought

256
00:22:57,020 --> 00:23:02,520
– means you get dissolved 
into yourself.

257
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:07,590
This is what is reality.

258
00:23:09,980 --> 00:23:15,890
But you are aware also; 
now that’s another point.

259
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:24,680
If you ask yourself a question 
you are not there,

260
00:23:26,320 --> 00:23:28,130
but you are aware.

261
00:23:28,900 --> 00:23:31,210
If your Nabhi is catching 
you immediately you know

262
00:23:31,450 --> 00:23:34,610
“My Nabhi is catching, 
I have got liver.”

