00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:37,390
Don’t have to ask questions.

264
00:23:37,670 --> 00:23:39,380
Or somebody is standing near you,

265
00:23:39,630 --> 00:23:43,890
his left Swadisthana 
– “Oh my God, it is this one!”

266
00:23:47,910 --> 00:23:50,030
If somebody is very angry 
and hot tempered,

267
00:23:50,340 --> 00:23:52,640
immediately you’ll feel such 
heat from that person,

268
00:23:52,900 --> 00:23:56,430
you’ll say, “Oh baba, 
I’ll run away from this man.”

269
00:23:57,350 --> 00:24:00,690
So this is a new

270
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:07,290
realm you have entered into reality,

271
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:11,560
which you are never aware of before.

272
00:24:12,730 --> 00:24:18,590
Now supposing there’s a very 
bad man standing near you.

273
00:24:19,450 --> 00:24:23,890
He might be a thief, he might 
be a murderer, anything

274
00:24:24,190 --> 00:24:27,250
– you will not be even 
conscious of it

275
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:30,880
leave alone aware, normally.

276
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:35,320
But once you are a realized soul,

277
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:42,850
you become aware of the whole.

278
00:24:43,190 --> 00:24:45,370
That is reality.

279
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:51,100
What are the problems, 
in the collective

280
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:55,930
you become aware of the collective.

281
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:59,430
You become aware of the 
problems of the whole world.

282
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:03,210
Now, this awareness is 
very different.

283
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:08,660
The first awareness as 
I told you is like this,

284
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:13,870
that if somebody tells you 
you are this and this,

285
00:25:14,210 --> 00:25:17,470
you become aware of it.

286
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:23,210
In this nobody has to tell you;

287
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:27,400
it’s just there.

288
00:25:31,360 --> 00:25:35,800
You are there, you know what it is.

289
00:25:37,630 --> 00:25:45,680
And this is what you have 
achieved in these modern times,

290
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:49,950
which is the blessing 
of the modern times also,

291
00:25:50,370 --> 00:25:55,330
that we know now who we are.

292
00:25:56,350 --> 00:26:01,580
You always say, “We are the pure 
spirit,” yesterday also I heard it.

293
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,910
Are you sure?

294
00:26:04,190 --> 00:26:07,970
What makes you believe that,

295
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:13,090
that you are the pure spirit?

296
00:26:14,060 --> 00:26:17,600
I mean, you haven’t seen 
your spirit, have you?

297
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:21,500
You haven’t seen yourself 
what you are.

298
00:26:22,190 --> 00:26:25,130
Then how do you say you 
are the pure spirit?

299
00:26:25,450 --> 00:26:31,850
It’s just you are saying 
something because I say so.

300
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:40,470
But you are the pure spirit, 
because whatever the description

301
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:43,220
of the pure spirit is given

302
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:47,770
that it is aware

303
00:26:48,790 --> 00:26:54,290
of the divine Power.

304
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:59,210
It is aware of the divine Power,

305
00:26:59,890 --> 00:27:04,210
and that is how you 
are the pure spirit;

306
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:08,040
because only 
through pure spirit

307
00:27:08,360 --> 00:27:11,020
as your personality

308
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:19,020
you can be aware of this 
all-pervading Power.

309
00:27:20,190 --> 00:27:27,340
This is written in all the shastras, 
in all the scriptures everywhere.

310
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:31,190
And what do you know 
about yourself?

311
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:40,020
– that you are the spirit, because 
you know about your own chakras,

312
00:27:40,530 --> 00:27:43,860
you know about your own nadis.

313
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:50,050
Now, what has happened is that 
you are separated from your self

314
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:54,450
and you can see your self.

315
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:59,650
You see yourself very clearly,

316
00:28:02,020 --> 00:28:11,250
and you start seeing yourself as the 
present and the past and the future.

317
00:28:12,490 --> 00:28:15,930
“In the past what I was” 
– you see, you’re shocked now

318
00:28:16,210 --> 00:28:18,730
“my goodness, I was like this.”

319
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:23,160
You see it through this 
present state,

320
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:26,570
in the present state you see.

321
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:33,890
Then you start forgetting it, 
“Forget the past, forget the past.”

322
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:40,810
Then still you have the future;

323
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:47,040
then you start thinking 
about the future.

324
00:28:47,970 --> 00:28:50,890
First, future they think 
about their own

325
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:54,290
children, their wives 
- Sahaja yogis also

326
00:28:54,650 --> 00:29:01,370
– “What will happen to my children, 
what will happen to my wife?”

327
00:29:02,530 --> 00:29:07,360
Then they think, “What will 
happen to Sahaja Yoga?”

328
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:12,320
Then they think, “What 
will happen to Mataji?”

329
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:17,860
Also they think, “What will 
happen to this world?”

330
00:29:19,360 --> 00:29:27,330
Because your awareness 
has expanded,

331
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:33,320
you are not in the limited 
sphere now anymore.

332
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:38,090
You can think of your children, 
you can think of your wife,

333
00:29:38,390 --> 00:29:41,870
also you can think 
of the whole world

334
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:47,540
and all the problems of 
the world you think about.

335
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:53,420
So you have reached 
that state, all right;

336
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:56,910
up to that state we are.

337
00:29:57,980 --> 00:30:00,870
Now what is the thing

338
00:30:03,040 --> 00:30:08,730
that covers up all this 
or gives you solutions,

339
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:13,380
say, for your children, for your 
family, your wife, everyone

340
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:16,070
– what is the solution?

341
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:22,960
Your Mother believes in giving 
solutions, not only the problems

342
00:30:24,150 --> 00:30:27,640
Because these days 
there are not problems

343
00:30:27,970 --> 00:30:31,710
that existed in the Navaratri.

344
00:30:33,430 --> 00:30:35,710
They no more exist,

345
00:30:36,020 --> 00:30:42,590
that you can take a sword 
in your hand and go and

346
00:30:42,870 --> 00:30:45,410
kill someone; no, it doesn’t,

347
00:30:46,330 --> 00:30:49,990
it’s not possible – cut what?

348
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:56,270
So the today’s problem 
as they are, as we see

349
00:30:58,010 --> 00:31:01,940
– within us we see the problems,

350
00:31:02,190 --> 00:31:06,960
we are aware of it and we 
want to do something about it.

351
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:11,250
Whether we are in the past, 
present or future,

352
00:31:11,530 --> 00:31:14,280
we see the problem.

353
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:21,540
So now what is the solution?

354
00:31:22,950 --> 00:31:31,020
We have no weapons, 
nothing to fight.

355
00:31:32,750 --> 00:31:34,930
We don’t know also, 
so many do not

356
00:31:35,210 --> 00:31:38,850
know even how to hold 
a sword in the hand,

357
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:42,610
nd so many don’t 
even want to hold it;

358
00:31:43,890 --> 00:31:46,730
because they are so 
much in compassion,

359
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:50,500
in the ocean of compassion 
enjoying themselves nicely.

360
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:55,290
They are enjoying their own 
compassion and compassion of others,

361
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:58,170
compassion of their Mother.

362
00:31:58,780 --> 00:32:02,300
But then how to solve the problem?

363
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:10,100
The problem can be solved

364
00:32:10,330 --> 00:32:15,710
if you become very 
powerful yourself within.

365
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:21,890
Where is your attention?

366
00:32:25,520 --> 00:32:28,410
You have to move inward.

367
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:31,240
Where is your attention?

368
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:36,690
You have to become very powerful.

369
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:42,490
I have done My job, I have 
given you realization.

370
00:32:43,470 --> 00:32:47,230
You have grown so much, 
I have explained to you,

371
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:50,280
I’ve told you everything 
– it’s done.

372
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:54,540
I have given you lots of love,

373
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:59,380
ocean of love I should say 
as you call it, whatever it is.

374
00:33:01,910 --> 00:33:05,510
But now you have to 
nourish yourself.

375
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:10,590
You have to become 
powerful within yourself.

376
00:33:13,460 --> 00:33:17,540
So what is the way you 
can become powerful?

377
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:25,020
First you must believe

378
00:33:25,290 --> 00:33:30,010
that you have transcended 
your human personality

379
00:33:30,290 --> 00:33:35,820
and you have now become 
a super-human being.

380
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:45,790
First of all this must come in.

381
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:49,390
This is what we call as faith.

382
00:33:50,150 --> 00:33:54,460
This faith is not false 
faith, is not blind faith

383
00:33:54,750 --> 00:34:00,620
that you believe into 
something, but it’s a fact.

384
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:05,530
I have a hundred times, 
I have told you

385
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:10,930
that you have first of all 
faith in your ascent

386
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:15,190
in your position as Sahaja yogis.

387
00:34:18,190 --> 00:34:21,680
For this meditation is 
very important,

388
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:24,940
very important.

389
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:31,140
Without meditation you cannot 
have full faith in yourself,

390
00:34:32,180 --> 00:34:34,980
because you can’t know yourself

391
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:39,040
by saying, “Who am I?” You cannot.

392
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:47,080
You try now, ask a question within, 
“Who am I?” – you’ll be lost.

393
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,970
So what 
should be the faith then?

394
00:34:56,210 --> 00:35:00,790
because when you ask the question 
“Who am I?” you are lost.

395
00:35:07,990 --> 00:35:11,520
So we reach a stage 
where I have to tell you

396
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:19,140
that faith is not mental, it is 
not emotional, it is not physical,

397
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:25,890
but it is a state of your own being

398
00:35:26,650 --> 00:35:31,370
which we can call as 
a spiritual state.

399
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:39,490
In the spiritual state

400
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:47,740
nothing can disturb you,

401
00:35:49,940 --> 00:35:53,190
nothing can overpower you,

402
00:35:54,010 --> 00:35:57,320
nothing can dominate you;

403
00:35:59,510 --> 00:36:02,910
because that state if you have,

404
00:36:03,270 --> 00:36:09,750
that means you are part 
and parcel of reality.

405
00:36:11,010 --> 00:36:18,890
Then you are a honored member 
of the God’s kingdom.

406
00:36:20,950 --> 00:36:29,780
Then you are the most 
revered personality.

407
00:36:31,370 --> 00:36:34,580
Then you are like a deity.

408
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:39,140
Then you are like a gana.

409
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:45,500
In that state when you are 
– it’s a state, again I say,

410
00:36:46,210 --> 00:36:49,860
beyond the human state

411
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:56,550
– you are extremely powerful.

412
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:06,750
There’s a story about 
Nizamuddin – great Auliya,

413
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:09,950
great Sufi in India.

414
00:37:10,390 --> 00:37:13,140
There was a horrible king

415
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:16,750
I think what Shah he called himself;

416
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:22,610
and he would not go and bow 
to him. So he was very angry.

417
00:37:22,890 --> 00:37:26,530
He said, “I can only bow 
to God and to nobody else.”

418
00:37:28,130 --> 00:37:32,120
This Shah said, “If you don’t come 
and bow to me tomorrow,

419
00:37:32,370 --> 00:37:35,620
I will cut your throat.”

420
00:37:36,350 --> 00:37:40,920
And that night, the throat 
of this king was cut.

421
00:37:41,900 --> 00:37:46,330
It’s a story, but it’s a real story.

422
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:53,670
Somebody came and cut his throat 
– it was not Nizamuddhin Sahib;

423
00:37:53,950 --> 00:37:57,080
he would not do that.

424
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:03,580
So that state if you reach,

425
00:38:05,010 --> 00:38:10,800
what we call is 
the state of shraddha,

426
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:18,410
state of shraddha

427
00:38:18,730 --> 00:38:25,160
which is enlightened, 
enlightened faith.

428
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:34,630
It’s a new type of mechanism;

429
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:44,700
that is, you become part 
and parcel of the whole.

430
00:38:45,850 --> 00:38:49,440
That means the moon, the star…see

431
00:38:50,470 --> 00:38:55,040
I tell you, I never told the sun that 
it should be there for the pujas,

432
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:57,960
I never told, last time, 
I never tell him.

433
00:38:58,270 --> 00:39:02,610
There’s no need to tell, 
it’s all done.

434
00:39:05,070 --> 00:39:08,660
I don’t tell all these vibrations

435
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:14,940
to make a cross or to show these, 
all these miraculous photographs.

436
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:18,740
I don’t there’s no need to tell;

437
00:39:21,820 --> 00:39:25,770
they just do it by themselves 
I am sometimes surprised

438
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:28,890
how ingenious methods 
they have of their own,

439
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:32,550
how they manage things 
– I am myself surprised.

440
00:39:33,590 --> 00:39:36,490
I didn’t tell them that 
these two persons

