00:39:36,770 --> 00:39:38,790
who were selected by this award

442
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:42,950
should be so condemned 
by every newspaper.

443
00:39:43,340 --> 00:39:46,650
It all works automatically,

444
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:52,880
it just works.

445
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:59,120
Only thing if I have anything is 
just complete, complete faith

446
00:39:59,390 --> 00:40:02,240
that I am at that state,

447
00:40:02,830 --> 00:40:07,530
and that’s why there is 
complete patience, saburi,

448
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:10,580
complete patience.

449
00:40:15,820 --> 00:40:19,630
And that is what we have to learn.

450
00:40:20,750 --> 00:40:26,840
It will all happen in any case 
because you are all at that state.

451
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:30,980
Only meditation is important, 
very important;

452
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:34,350
for Me not, but for you all.

