00:40:35,210 --> 00:40:38,190
If you all can meditate now,

454
00:40:38,810 --> 00:40:45,990
just for ten minutes also every day,

455
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:49,370
it will help you a lot.

456
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:57,050
Now, why do we have all these 
statues and, I mean the Mother

457
00:40:57,620 --> 00:41:02,500
and the Hanumana 
and Ganesha, Christ?

458
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:06,340
Because to begin with, 
human beings cannot

