00:42:25,060 --> 00:42:29,810
Unless and until you know 
the absolute truth,

476
00:42:30,830 --> 00:42:32,770
you are nowhere;

477
00:42:33,350 --> 00:42:39,150
you have no discretion, you have no 
understanding, you have no wisdom.

478
00:42:40,430 --> 00:42:43,110
But once you know the absolute truth,

479
00:42:43,450 --> 00:42:48,800
then you should not by any chance

480
00:42:49,710 --> 00:42:52,660
be halfway this and halfway that.

481
00:42:53,360 --> 00:43:00,290
That’s a very dangerous 
state of affairs.

482
00:43:00,650 --> 00:43:08,040
Say a seed is sprouted, it is 
neither a seed nor a tree.

483
00:43:10,730 --> 00:43:14,620
If it doesn’t grow it is useless.

484
00:43:15,060 --> 00:43:18,320
That’s happens to your 
awareness – I am again talking

485
00:43:18,640 --> 00:43:21,920
of your consciousness, awareness

486
00:43:25,470 --> 00:43:31,260
– and then you are neither 
here nor there.

487
00:43:31,870 --> 00:43:38,610
There are many people who come 
to Sahaja Yoga perhaps, maybe

488
00:43:39,360 --> 00:43:42,510
to find some peace.

