00:44:03,670 --> 00:44:06,420
my art is not selling.”

496
00:44:06,700 --> 00:44:11,750
All these stupid problems 
they bring for Me.

497
00:44:12,080 --> 00:44:17,240
Hah – “My children are no good, 
they are troublesome.”

498
00:44:17,530 --> 00:44:19,460
Then, “My wife is fighting with me,

499
00:44:19,720 --> 00:44:22,400
my mother is fighting with 
me, brother is fighting.”

500
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:27,220
But I said, “What sort 
of Sahaja yogis these are?”

501
00:44:31,330 --> 00:44:36,810
The state of being one 
with the reality

502
00:44:39,630 --> 00:44:45,570
means that the whole 
of reality is at your feet,

503
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:49,770
whole of it works for you;

504
00:44:50,730 --> 00:44:55,730
and once you even 
get a glimpse of that state

505
00:44:56,010 --> 00:45:03,230
I tell you, you become so much 
peaceful within yourself.

506
00:45:08,600 --> 00:45:12,400
If you say, “I am the king, 
I am the king,”

507
00:45:12,850 --> 00:45:15,940
if you say, “I am the beggar, 
I am the beggar,”

508
00:45:16,260 --> 00:45:19,400
what difference does it 
make to that state

509
00:45:19,690 --> 00:45:24,880
which is like a purest of pure gold,

510
00:45:25,340 --> 00:45:28,990
which cannot be tarnished?

511
00:45:32,280 --> 00:45:36,100
Such a state of mind 
we have to develop.

512
00:45:37,530 --> 00:45:41,350
It’s a more a challenge to us.

513
00:45:42,090 --> 00:45:44,970
We are Sahaja yogis, all right.

514
00:45:45,610 --> 00:45:48,560
We have got realization, all right.

515
00:45:49,190 --> 00:45:52,310
We can sing very well, all right.

516
00:45:52,670 --> 00:45:56,100
We have achieved good 
positions, all right.

517
00:45:57,030 --> 00:46:00,000
We are nicely married, all right.

518
00:46:00,570 --> 00:46:03,470
We’ve got nice children, 
we have got everything,

519
00:46:03,740 --> 00:46:05,960
we have got jobs, this that.

520
00:46:06,280 --> 00:46:13,160
Now, suddenly one negative force 
comes in to trouble you – so what?

521
00:46:16,890 --> 00:46:18,890
So what?

522
00:46:22,030 --> 00:46:26,630
Otherwise how will you 
know what you are?

523
00:46:28,120 --> 00:46:32,490
If there is no darkness, how will 
you know you are the light?

524
00:46:34,730 --> 00:46:44,670
It’s a challenge to your own 
state, at what state you are.

525
00:46:45,630 --> 00:46:51,090
The word “state” is not so 
explanatory. In Sanskrit is swarupa,

526
00:46:51,510 --> 00:46:53,710
swarupa

527
00:46:56,640 --> 00:47:03,550
– “swa” is yourself 
and “rupa” is form or state.

528
00:47:05,270 --> 00:47:11,310
That state is possible 
for all of you

529
00:47:13,460 --> 00:47:18,290
by saying “Not this, not this, 
not this, not this.”

530
00:47:21,230 --> 00:47:28,460
As it is, your mind has reached 
that state that there is no mind

531
00:47:28,790 --> 00:47:31,130
– you can do that.

532
00:47:31,790 --> 00:47:38,060
But you have to develop 
a kind of a personality

533
00:47:38,510 --> 00:47:42,290
that realizes what you are.

534
00:47:45,500 --> 00:47:49,240
But in that realization

535
00:47:51,430 --> 00:47:54,340
you are just aware of it,

536
00:47:54,630 --> 00:47:56,610
not conscious of it.

537
00:47:56,930 --> 00:47:59,610
Ah, for example I’ll tell you,

538
00:48:00,800 --> 00:48:04,690
I am aware that I am Adi Shakti 
– I am aware, I know.

539
00:48:05,050 --> 00:48:10,420
But when you say “Jai Shri Mataji” 
I also say “Jai Shri Mataji,”

540
00:48:10,710 --> 00:48:15,220
forgetting that I am the 
one you are talking about.

541
00:48:18,070 --> 00:48:23,490
This is actually, 
should be the state:

542
00:48:24,680 --> 00:48:28,330
that you are aware, yes, you 
are aware in the sense, in the

543
00:48:28,600 --> 00:48:32,100
- I don’t know how to say 
- but I am aware I am that.

544
00:48:32,350 --> 00:48:34,760
If you ask Me, “Mother, 
are You Adi Shakti?”

545
00:48:35,020 --> 00:48:41,680
I said, “Yes, I am” - because 
I know that, that I am.

546
00:48:42,090 --> 00:48:45,400
But when you say 
“Jai Shri Mataji” I forget that

547
00:48:45,650 --> 00:48:50,690
I am Adi Shakti and I also say 
“Jai Shri Mataji” with you.

548
00:48:54,350 --> 00:48:57,770
I forget; I have to tell, 
“No, no, You can’t say

549
00:49:01,380 --> 00:49:02,670
It’s very interesting.

550
00:49:02,980 --> 00:49:06,720
Now, you make Me sit 
here like a queen

551
00:49:07,040 --> 00:49:09,820
and give Me a presents, 
this thing, that thing;

552
00:49:10,090 --> 00:49:14,410
I mean, all right, that’s your idea.

553
00:49:17,780 --> 00:49:26,240
But to Me, you see, I am 
complete in Myself, I think so.

554
00:49:28,390 --> 00:49:33,510
This in Hindi: “Me kahenge ki 
hum apne hi andar samma gaye”

555
00:49:34,670 --> 00:49:40,030
- “ I am got lost into Myself.”

556
00:49:40,300 --> 00:49:43,680
All right, you do this, all right; 
you should do that, all right.

557
00:49:43,960 --> 00:49:47,300
If you don’t do it, it’s all right.

558
00:49:48,950 --> 00:49:52,660
To Me it makes no difference; 
it may make difference to you,

559
00:49:53,020 --> 00:49:54,950
but to Me it does not.

560
00:49:55,240 --> 00:49:57,770
I have been saying that don’t 
give Me any presents,

561
00:49:58,000 --> 00:50:00,320
don’t give Me any 
presents, all these days.

562
00:50:00,690 --> 00:50:02,580
So the only argument is that

563
00:50:02,840 --> 00:50:06,380
“In whole year we give You once, 
so why should You, Mother, object?

564
00:50:06,640 --> 00:50:08,450
because that gives us joy.”

565
00:50:08,720 --> 00:50:11,480
All right, if you think 
it gives you joy, do it,

566
00:50:11,790 --> 00:50:15,160
but to Me it doesn’t matter.

567
00:50:19,370 --> 00:50:22,990
Because I don’t think I am there.

568
00:50:25,470 --> 00:50:30,490
I am just seeing you 
sitting here, all right

569
00:50:30,760 --> 00:50:34,260
– they are all realized souls, all right

570
00:50:36,750 --> 00:50:39,420
– but I am one of you.

571
00:50:40,730 --> 00:50:43,670
I don’t think I am very special.

572
00:50:44,410 --> 00:50:48,980
But if you ask Me then I will say, 
“All right, I am Adi Shakti.”

573
00:50:49,250 --> 00:50:52,860
But I don’t think Adi Shakti 
is very special also,

574
00:50:56,160 --> 00:50:58,460
because I’ve no mind.

575
00:50:58,770 --> 00:51:01,060
But otherwise I don’t think 
it’s something special;

576
00:51:01,320 --> 00:51:04,720
because somebody is 
something, so what?

577
00:51:05,790 --> 00:51:11,320
Now supposing sun is 
sun, so what? – He’s a sun.

578
00:51:12,570 --> 00:51:16,250
If somebody is Adi Shakti 
– so Adi Shakti, so what?

579
00:51:18,060 --> 00:51:20,700
But for you it is creditable

580
00:51:20,930 --> 00:51:27,560
because you were not born 
realized, you got your realization.

581
00:51:28,560 --> 00:51:33,150
So you are special, you are great,

582
00:51:33,410 --> 00:51:35,610
you have achieved something. 
I’ve achieved nothing;

583
00:51:35,860 --> 00:51:39,530
I have been like this and 
I will be like this.

584
00:51:42,670 --> 00:51:45,920
Whether I fight the devils 
or I sit before

585
00:51:46,150 --> 00:51:48,970
you makes no difference, 
I will be like this.

586
00:51:49,220 --> 00:51:54,840
But for Me you are great, 
because you have achieved this.

587
00:51:55,180 --> 00:51:58,970
Today to see you 
on this Navaratri day,

588
00:51:59,200 --> 00:52:03,400
so many people sitting 
to worship Me;

589
00:52:05,870 --> 00:52:08,770
so many people are here,

590
00:52:09,040 --> 00:52:13,880
so many Sahaja yogis 
- it’s so remarkable.

591
00:52:14,390 --> 00:52:16,880
It’s not My achievement I tell you,

592
00:52:17,100 --> 00:52:18,930
it’s your seeking.

593
00:52:19,150 --> 00:52:22,590
Because I have been on this 
earth many a times before

594
00:52:24,650 --> 00:52:26,350
that you know.

595
00:52:27,120 --> 00:52:29,330
But we never had like this.

596
00:52:29,610 --> 00:52:33,310
So many came, got crucified, 
died, this, that,

597
00:52:33,550 --> 00:52:36,510
but I never had people of this kind.

598
00:52:38,980 --> 00:52:42,500
So again we come 
to the same point,

599
00:52:43,110 --> 00:52:50,510
that we should be aware 
of ourselves

600
00:52:52,140 --> 00:52:55,040
– complete shraddha 
in yourself.

601
00:52:55,760 --> 00:52:59,190
If you have some shraddha 
in yourself,

602
00:52:59,500 --> 00:53:02,320
you’ll have shraddha about Me also,

603
00:53:02,980 --> 00:53:06,940
because we are not different.

604
00:53:09,130 --> 00:53:11,900
If you believe this is water,

605
00:53:12,170 --> 00:53:13,500
then everywhere there is water

606
00:53:13,740 --> 00:53:16,820
I believe that that is 
water, isn’t it?

607
00:53:17,140 --> 00:53:19,910
Because I know this is water,

608
00:53:20,920 --> 00:53:25,320
so wherever in the world there 
is water, I know it is water.

609
00:53:26,740 --> 00:53:29,560
So if you know you are 
a Sahaja yogi,

610
00:53:29,980 --> 00:53:35,270
anywhere there is a Sahaja yogi 
you know there is a Sahaja yogi,

611
00:53:36,930 --> 00:53:41,100
But as far as you are 
concerned you forget

612
00:53:42,920 --> 00:53:47,290
how great you are, 
and how far you can go.

613
00:53:47,610 --> 00:53:50,810
I am very proud of you, 
you don’t know.

614
00:53:51,080 --> 00:53:55,940
But because I am a humble person,

615
00:53:57,080 --> 00:53:59,910
I don’t know how to show off

616
00:54:01,590 --> 00:54:07,880
– so I have such nice children, 
so many of them, so lovable.

617
00:54:10,390 --> 00:54:16,100
Those bhaktas for whom She killed 
so many demons and all that

618
00:54:17,880 --> 00:54:20,200
were not like you.

619
00:54:21,090 --> 00:54:24,100
You are much better, 
much higher,

620
00:54:24,490 --> 00:54:26,730
of a much greater quality.

621
00:54:27,010 --> 00:54:31,210
But you must know that you are,

622
00:54:31,530 --> 00:54:37,310
and don’t behave like 
those people who

623
00:54:37,630 --> 00:54:42,320
were of a very rudimentary nature.

624
00:54:42,820 --> 00:54:46,870
You are grown up, 
you have prospered,

625
00:54:47,300 --> 00:54:51,120
and now the fruits we can see.

626
00:54:53,400 --> 00:54:56,630
I don’t know what to 
do for you, really.

627
00:54:57,010 --> 00:55:00,790
But have faith in yourself.

628
00:55:02,930 --> 00:55:07,010
Then you will see how much 
faith you will have in reality,

629
00:55:07,250 --> 00:55:10,790
that there is reality with 
you at every step,

630
00:55:11,030 --> 00:55:13,710
every moment.

631
00:55:17,250 --> 00:55:19,350
No fear,

632
00:55:22,590 --> 00:55:25,460
no sense of achievement - nothing.

633
00:55:26,840 --> 00:55:29,000
Done now, finished.

634
00:55:30,510 --> 00:55:32,570
When there were five 
Sahaja yogis I was happy,

635
00:55:32,780 --> 00:55:34,610
when there are so many, I am happy.

636
00:55:34,870 --> 00:55:39,850
But I, when I see so many, I think

637
00:55:41,640 --> 00:55:49,100
there are so many powerful 
personalities who are one with reality.

638
00:55:51,240 --> 00:55:57,730
This collective oneness 
was never so.

639
00:55:59,260 --> 00:56:05,140
And so I would say that on this day

640
00:56:05,700 --> 00:56:09,840
what we have to do is to 
kill the devils within ourselves;

641
00:56:12,330 --> 00:56:14,150
that’s all.

642
00:56:15,550 --> 00:56:18,450
If you want to really worship Me,

643
00:56:18,660 --> 00:56:23,040
that’s what you have to think, 
what are the devils within you

644
00:56:23,600 --> 00:56:25,110
– that’s all.

645
00:56:25,430 --> 00:56:28,090
So you don’t have to worry 
otherwise for outside devils,

646
00:56:28,350 --> 00:56:30,810
they cannot do anything to you.

647
00:56:33,950 --> 00:56:36,310
May God bless you.
